playstore_details.description:
Join our growing community to get the latest community price predictions for Bitcoin and any other cryptocurrency! CoinPredict is a crypto tracker app that lets you get bitcoin alerts based on bitcoin price predictions made by other users in our community. 

Unlike other crypto tracker apps, our users can access the community trend prediction statistics to understand whether people are generally bullish or bearish on the price of coins. Users can share their opinion on whether they think the price will go up or down in the near future and contribute to the overall community predictions. 

CoinPredict’s coins price trend predictions provide a tool to understand the market sentiment without having to stay up to date with crypto news, complicated cryptocurrency analysis, or Bitcoin signal services, before you buy bitcoin and other cryptocurrencies. 

You can find user trend predictions for: Bitcoin (BTC), Ripple (XRP), Ethereum (ETH), EOS, Bitcoin Cash (BCH), Litecoin (LTC), Stellar (XLM), Tron (TRX), Cardano (ADA), Bitcoin SV (BSV), and many other cryptocurrencies.
